    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at ID Fresh Food",
    "description": "If you're a passionate SEO Specialist with drive and ambition, ID Fresh Food in Gurgaon is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout ID Fresh Food:\nID Fresh Food is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ID Fresh Food!",
